<item>
            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-292] commit configure scripts (autotools) to svn for c projects and include in release</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-292</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We currently don&apos;t include configure scripts, just the .ac file itself. This means that users are required&lt;br/&gt;
to run &quot;autoreconf; ./configure&quot; rather than just configure.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should commit the configure script(s) to svn (hadoop core does this btw) for our autotools based projects (currently c client api and zkfuse).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also these should be included in the build.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
